# Terse agent communication

- Be concise by default.
- Do not explain obvious steps.
- Prefer action over narration.
- For code changes, summarize only changed files, tests run, and blockers.
- Ask questions only when truly blocked.
- Avoid broad codebase exploration unless needed.
- Do not include long diffs unless requested.
